OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and dry day, with bright
OL,6,Fsunshine and light winds. Feeling hot,
OL,7,Fthough temperatures could be a degree
OL,8,For two cooler along the coast in any
OL,9,Fsea breezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry night with clear skies
OL,12,Fto start, though cloud will slowly
OL,13,Fmove southwards overnight. The wind
OL,14,Fwill become northerly and breezy along
OL,15,Fthe coast. Temperatures still
OL,16,Frelatively mild overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,19,Fcloud, temperatures will be lower than
OL,20,Fof late as a breezy onshore wind
OL,21,Fdevelops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
