OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry with variable cloud on
OL,7,FWednesday. Cloudier with showers
OL,8,Fpossible on Thursday. Remaining cloudy
OL,9,Fon Friday, breezy along the coast.
OL,10,FTemperatures remain warm but feeling
OL,11,Fcooler along the coasts.
